    Who We Are

    Aidios Bridgeway is a leading provider of renewable energy solutions based in Nigeria, West Africa. Our mission is to empower businesses and consumers to achieve transition to sustainable eco-friendly energy choices by offering top-notch renewable energy solutions delivered with first-class services.

    With a team of experienced professionals and a commitment to quality, we ensure every project is executed with precision and care. Our innovative solutions address the following:

    • Impact of grid related challenges
    • Offer cost savings and improves efficiency
    • Helps in reducing carbon footprint

    At Aidios Bridgeway, we believe in a greener future and are dedicated to making renewable energy accessible to and for all. Join us in our journey towards sustainability and make a positive impact on our environment.

    Solutions

    Comprehensive energy storage solutions for every sector

    Telecom Titan

    Advanced engineered Lithium-ion Telecoms UPS systems. Rack mountable and uniquely able to integrate with and/or replace existing lead acid battery solutions in cell tower infrastructure. Unleash the power of Lithium battery energy storage for unstoppable telecom performance.

    C&I Champion

    Modular cabinets and containerised solutions able to support Commercial and Industrial (C&I) Areas, Factories, EVC Stations, Grid Application and Renewable pairing. Elevate your business with cutting-edge energy solutions tailored for commercial success.

    Residential Resilience

    All-In-One systems with Lithium-ion battery and integrated inverter for residential home usage. Transform your home into a fortress of energy independence with our residential packages.
